Hello! Thank you for calling Sparkle Dry Cleaners. My name is Alex. How may I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I wanted to inquire about your services.

Of course! May I have your name, please?

Sure, it's Jamie.

Perfect! Thank you so much, Jamie. Is there anything else you'd like to know about our services?

No, that answers my questions. Thank you, Alex.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for reaching out to Sparkle Dry Cleaners. Have a great day!
